      <ab type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">The picture shows the entrance of the ‘Patria’ cinema with an advertisement for a movie above. In front of the building is a tram in poor condition.</ab>
      <ab subtype="comment" type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">The cinema, located at 12–14 Bulevardul Magheru, is among the best-known movie theatres in Bucharest. It is housed in the modernist ten-storey ‘Asigurarea Românească’ building, designed in 1929 and completed in 1931. The photograph was taken in 1954.</ab>
